# Jarvis

Jarvis is an open-source AI assistant platform currently under development.

## Vision
The goal of Jarvis is to build a modular AI ecosystem that helps people automate work and create AI-powered applications.

## Planned Features
- AI chat assistant
- AI coding assistant
- Workflow automation
- Content creation tools
- Image and video AI integration
- API support
- Multi-agent architecture
- Plugin system

## Current Status
This project is in active development. New features will be added over time, and community contributions are welcome.

